CREATE TABLE properties (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    address VARCHAR(255),
    square_footage INT,
    amenities TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE properties (id INT PRIMARY KEY, address VARCHAR(255), square_footage INT, amenities VARCHAR(255));

CREATE TABLE images (id INT PRIMARY KEY, property_id INT, image_url VARCHAR(255));

CREATE TABLE listing (
    listing_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    property_id INT,
    agent_id INT,
    price DECIMAL(10,2),
    date_listed DATE,
    status VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE listings (
  listing_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  property_id INT,
  agent_id INT,
  price DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL,
  status VARCHAR(20) DEFAULT 'Active'
);
